Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.32,0:00:05.23,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.23,0:00:06.98,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,It's because you're wearing all that!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.77,0:00:09.58,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,What's the big deal?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.58,0:00:10.73,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,It's over anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.73,0:00:11.57,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's not!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.57,0:00:14.32,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,There's gonna be a jump-rope \Ncontest on the return trip, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.32,0:00:16.28,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,You saw the red meat that \Nthe winning team got!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.91,0:00:21.40,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,We can't take last place again!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.40,0:00:23.65,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,We need to pull out of fish tier, at least!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.65,0:00:24.87,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,It's not red meat!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.00,0:00:34.61,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.61,0:00:37.17,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Shirase-chan, you're quite \Nadept at jumping rope.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.17,0:00:38.14,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,Is that weird?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.14,0:00:41.91,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,No, but you just didn't seem like the type.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.91,0:00:42.71,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.71,0:00:45.88,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Defying expectations is kind \Nof Shirase-chan's thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.88,0:00:47.50,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Like, she's clumsier than she looks.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.50,0:00:49.24,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,More short-tempered than she looks.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.24,0:00:51.32,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,More selfish than she looks.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.32,0:00:53.00,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,What's that supposed to mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.36,0:00:59.61,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Someone's birthday?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.78,0:01:04.96,Main,toshi,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.17,0:01:11.96,Main,toshi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm in love!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.60,0:01:28.15,Show_Title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(2280,1225)}A Place Further Than the Universe
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.01,0:02:50.52,Ep_Title,sign,0000,0000,0000,,Antarctic Love Story\N(Blizzard Arc)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.01,0:02:50.52,Likes/Comments,sign,0000,0000,0000,,30 Likes\N1 Comment
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.01,0:02:50.52,Hashtags,sign,0000,0000,0000,,#HowsTheLoveLife #CantPutItIntoWords
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.52,0:02:52.27,sign_6829_70_High_School_Girl,sign,0000,0000,0000,,High School Girls' room!!\NYou gotta {\c&H4EE8E2&}KNOCK
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.57,0:02:52.27,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,You're in love?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.49,0:02:53.93,Main,kimari,0000,0000,0000,,With the team captain?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.93,0:02:55.04,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.04,0:02:56.28,Main,toshi,0000,0000,0000,,Zaizen Toshio.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.72,0:02:58.79,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You're{\i0} in love with her?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.79,0:02:59.48,Main,toshi,0000,0000,0000,,Something wrong with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.48,0:03:01.76,Main,yumi,0000,0000,0000,,Of course there's something wrong with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.76,0:03:05.08,Main,yumi,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone you tell gets so exasperated \Nthey lose their capacity for words.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.40,0:03:06.46,Main,yumi,0000,0000,0000,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.46,0:03:07.64,Main,toshi,0000,0000,0000,,You're wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.64,0:03:09.56,Main,toshi,0000,0000,0000,,They're just so stunned \Nby my sudden confession...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.56,0:03:11.25,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,We're too exasperated to speak.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.25,0:03:12.21,Main,toshi,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.21,0:03:15.45,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,By team captain, you mean Captain Todo Gin?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.45,0:03:17.46,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,The beautiful, smart, determined...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.73,0:03:19.67,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Seems pretty out of your league.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.67,0:03:20.59,Main,toshi,0000,0000,0000,,That's so rude!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.59,0:03:22.52,Main,toshi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm allowed to be in love with someone!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.52,0:03:25.35,Main,toshi,0000,0000,0000,,I've always loved strong women like her!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.35,0:03:26.47,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.47,0:03:29.17,Main,toshi,0000,0000,0000,,I feel like... they could protect me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.34,0:03:31.44,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,You could just die.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.44,0:03:34.21,Main,toshi,0000,0000,0000,,Did you just say something to me? \NSomething truly cruel?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.21,0:03:35.82,Main,yumi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.82,0:03:38.64,Main,yumi,0000,0000,0000,,You said it before, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.64,0:03:40.65,Main,yumi,0000,0000,0000,,That you wouldn't bring romance onto the ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.65,0:03:42.72,Main,toshi,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I've held back until now!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.72,0:03:44.03,Main,toshi,0000,0000,0000,,But I can no longer stop myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.99,0:03:46.44,Main,yumi,0000,0000,0000,,I would love to hit you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.44,0:03:48.66,Main,toshi,0000,0000,0000,,You basically are hitting me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.97,0:03:51.54,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,So, why did you come to us?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.07,0:03:57.88,Main,toshi,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I heard that the captain had an \Nold friend among the high-schoolers...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.88,0:04:00.42,Main,toshi,0000,0000,0000,,I was wondering if you had any information...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.42,0:04:01.78,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,He means Shirase-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.78,0:04:03.45,Main,yumi,0000,0000,0000,,How long have you known her?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.31,0:04:08.21,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,I first met her about ten years ago, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.21,0:04:09.27,Main,toshi,0000,0000,0000,,Got any pictures from that time?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.27,0:04:12.06,Main,yumi,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, you need to maintain a \Nfive-meter distance at all times.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.06,0:04:13.31,Main,toshi,0000,0000,0000,,When was that decided?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.00,0:04:16.89,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,But she was just a friend of my mother's.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.89,0:04:18.73,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,I never talked to her much.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.08,0:04:21.10,Main,toshi,0000,0000,0000,,I see. Then what am I going to—
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.10,0:04:23.77,Main,yumi,0000,0000,0000,,Just give up on her, like I said!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.77,0:04:25.11,Main,yumi,0000,0000,0000,,Toshio, you're such a—
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.11,0:04:26.15,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.78,0:04:27.83,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.83,0:04:31.29,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Including the expedition members' love lives \Nin our reports will make them more exciting!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.57,0:04:32.41,Main,toshi,0000,0000,0000,,Report?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.80,0:04:35.14,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,I see! That's a great idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.14,0:04:37.20,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,We've never even touched on it before!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.20,0:04:37.95,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that in poor taste?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.95,0:04:38.88,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.88,0:04:41.80,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently our views have \Nbeen in the pits lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.80,0:04:43.15,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,You think people will watch?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.15,0:04:44.29,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,Of course they will!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.29,0:04:47.15,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever they might claim, \Neverybody loves things like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.56,0:04:49.51,Main,toshi,0000,0000,0000,,You mean, my love for the captain will...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.56,0:04:52.98,Main,toshi,0000,0000,0000,,...be broadcast to the whole \Nworld over the Internet?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.98,0:04:55.98,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,No, Zaizen-san, you can go back to your room.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.50,0:04:57.98,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,We'll take it from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.64,0:05:01.36,Main,yumi,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds like you're in the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.36,0:05:03.86,sign_7226_90_A_Gift_From_Peng,sign,0000,0000,0000,,A Gift From Penguin Farms!!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.36,0:05:03.86,sign_7226_91_Soft_Serve_Day,sign,0000,0000,0000,,Soft-Serve Day
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.36,0:05:03.86,sign_7226_92_Come_eat_,sign,0000,0000,0000,,Come eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.46,0:05:03.86,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of person she was?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.86,0:05:07.65,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! The captain's personality, \Nher relationships with men...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.65,0:05:12.49,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,I told you before. She was just someone \Nmy mom knew. I didn't especially...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.40,0:05:15.96,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,She never really talked much.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.72,0:05:19.33,Flashback,taka,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna buy some cabbage. Look after her.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.33,0:05:20.96,Flashback,gin,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! What should I...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.84,0:05:26.51,Flashback,shira,0000,0000,0000,,Here, your change.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.87,0:05:29.76,Flashback,shira,0000,0000,0000,,Here, your change.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.00,0:05:33.47,Flashback,gin,0000,0000,0000,,You shouldn't give money \Nto people you don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.98,0:05:37.01,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.01,0:05:39.19,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds more eccentric to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.19,0:05:41.02,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,So, what about her love life?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.19,0:05:44.01,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,How would I know about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.01,0:05:45.86,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,I was still in kindergarten back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.63,0:05:49.20,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,We'll just have to ask her ourselves, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.42,0:05:50.47,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,Ourselves?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.47,0:05:54.83,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,We'll set up an interview, and lead \Nthe conversation in that direction.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.83,0:05:57.83,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Like a press conference with a celebrity!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.83,0:05:59.58,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,"How's the love life?"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.94,0:06:01.43,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you asking me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.55,0:06:05.02,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, who's supposed to go ask her?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.84,0:06:08.09,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,No! No!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.32,0:06:10.82,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,I feel like we've been through this before!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.82,0:06:12.25,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,Have we really?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.25,0:06:13.87,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you so desperate not to do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.87,0:06:16.88,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,You talked to her on the deck \Nbefore we set out, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.88,0:06:17.64,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,You were watching?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.64,0:06:18.98,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Why would you ever think we weren't?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.98,0:06:21.07,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,You seemed close enough to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.07,0:06:23.17,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,No, we just happened to \Nrun into each other, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.17,0:06:24.69,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,You don't get along then?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.69,0:06:27.65,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know if I'd say. It's more like...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.01,0:06:29.24,Main,gin,0000,0000,0000,,There's a distance between us.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.55,0:06:32.39,Main,kana,0000,0000,0000,,You talked to her on the \Ndeck before, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.39,0:06:33.48,Main,gin,0000,0000,0000,,You saw that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.48,0:06:35.37,Main,kana,0000,0000,0000,,You seemed close enough to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.80,0:06:38.79,Main,gin,0000,0000,0000,,No, we just happened to \Nrun into each other, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.63,0:06:42.34,Main,gin,0000,0000,0000,,We always had trouble \Ncommunicating with each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.34,0:06:45.19,Main,gin,0000,0000,0000,,So whenever Takako would leave, we'd just...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.12,0:06:48.26,Flashback,both,0000,0000,0000,,A penguin!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.57,0:06:51.59,Main,kana,0000,0000,0000,,What on earth?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.96,0:06:54.13,Main,gin,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have any children,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.13,0:06:57.91,Main,gin,0000,0000,0000,,so I had no idea what to even say to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.91,0:06:59.16,Main,gin,0000,0000,0000,,Takako was just determined to—
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.16,0:07:01.23,Main,kana,0000,0000,0000,,But Takako's gone now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.34,0:07:05.28,Main,kana,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure you don't want to talk to her?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.71,0:07:06.95,Main,kana,0000,0000,0000,,About Takako?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.43,0:07:12.07,Main,kana,0000,0000,0000,,She's said that... that her \Nmother is waiting for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.03,0:07:20.96,Flashback,gin,0000,0000,0000,,We canceled the search.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.89,0:07:23.27,Flashback,gin,0000,0000,0000,,It was my call.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.98,0:07:31.46,Main,kana,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry for the wait. You can come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.01,0:07:32.87,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.87,0:07:35.01,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to impose...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.01,0:07:36.26,Main,kana,0000,0000,0000,,No problem!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.67,0:07:37.00,Main,gin,0000,0000,0000,,K-Kanae?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.50,0:07:38.52,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,Pardon us!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.34,0:07:41.89,Main,kana,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Shirase-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.72,0:07:44.83,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,She had something else to take care of.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.34,0:07:46.69,Main,kana,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.59,0:07:51.72,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, camera's rolling.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.50,0:07:55.16,Main,gin,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a minute. What are you going to ask me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.16,0:07:59.37,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,We were hoping to ask some questions \Nabout your personal life!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.68,0:08:02.79,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Your favorite foods, what you do back home...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.79,0:08:05.08,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,And... your love life!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.88,0:08:07.88,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,What's your "type"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.82,0:08:11.60,Main,gin,0000,0000,0000,,I will not answer questions unrelated \Nto the Antarctic expedition.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.60,0:08:14.64,Main,kana,0000,0000,0000,,Gin-chan, the high school \Ngirls have questions for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.64,0:08:16.26,Main,trio,0000,0000,0000,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.85,0:08:19.12,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,Our views have been dropping lately!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.12,0:08:20.94,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,We need this!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.64,0:08:22.85,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Her ears are bright red!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.59,0:08:24.60,Main,gin,0000,0000,0000,,They are not!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.60,0:08:26.39,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Captain, did you just get out of the bath?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.39,0:08:27.50,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,What's your favorite bath salt?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.50,0:08:29.23,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,What's your "type"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.43,0:08:33.24,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe we should make the \Neyes a little larger...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.24,0:08:36.23,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,I think she's fine the way she is...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.15,0:08:39.50,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,They're so big!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.50,0:08:42.71,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,They did say we were in the Antarctic Circle.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.49,0:08:48.16,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,The sun's not gonna go down, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.51,0:08:51.39,Main,toshi,0000,0000,0000,,Someone like a cloud?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.39,0:08:52.31,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,What does that mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.31,0:08:55.18,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Dunno. But that's what she said.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.43,0:08:57.43,Main,toshi,0000,0000,0000,,There are lots of kinds of clouds...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.43,0:09:01.43,Main,toshi,0000,0000,0000,,Cirrus, stratus, cumulus...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.43,0:09:02.37,Main,yumi,0000,0000,0000,,You're so boring.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.37,0:09:03.63,Main,toshi,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.11,0:09:05.10,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,I think...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.11,0:09:11.89,Flashback,taka,0000,0000,0000,,What big clouds!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.89,0:09:12.87,Flashback,shira,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.46,0:09:15.49,Flashback,gin,0000,0000,0000,,Clouds are amazing, aren't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.80,0:09:19.42,Flashback,gin,0000,0000,0000,,You can't grasp them, but when you \Nlook up, they're always there.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.42,0:09:24.50,Main,toshi,0000,0000,0000,,And... what does that mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.50,0:09:26.23,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.23,0:09:29.39,Main,gin,0000,0000,0000,,I think I have an idea, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.39,0:09:30.88,Main,yumi,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.30,0:09:39.85,Main,toshi,0000,0000,0000,,What? What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.89,0:09:46.60,Main,muka,0000,0000,0000,,How did the interview go?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.98,0:09:50.06,Main,gin,0000,0000,0000,,Did Kanae...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.28,0:09:52.90,Main,muka,0000,0000,0000,,No, I asked.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.90,0:09:55.42,Main,muka,0000,0000,0000,,I was just curious to know
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.42,0:09:58.89,Main,muka,0000,0000,0000,,if you and Kobuchizawa-san's \Ndaughter were very close.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.31,0:10:02.59,Main,gin,0000,0000,0000,,She didn't show up.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.54,0:10:08.36,Main,gin,0000,0000,0000,,She probably hasn't forgiven me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.33,0:10:12.66,Main,muka,0000,0000,0000,,That is a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.66,0:10:16.84,Main,muka,0000,0000,0000,,A captain needs to be able to talk \Nto their members and check in.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.21,0:10:24.85,Italics,vo,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}From 0800 hours to 1200 hours, \Ntraining is permitted on-deck.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.20,0:10:30.23,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.64,0:10:32.92,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,That looked like it hurt!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.92,0:10:34.98,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,That happens a lot when \Nyou exercise in winter...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.48,0:10:42.12,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Shirase?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.09,0:10:50.27,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,Penguins!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.67,0:10:59.97,Main,toshi,0000,0000,0000,,You know what it means? \NTo be "like a cloud"...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.92,0:11:02.92,Main,dai,0000,0000,0000,,I think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.92,0:11:04.35,Main,toshi,0000,0000,0000,,No way! What does it mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.66,0:11:07.47,Main,toshi,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me! What does it mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.02,0:11:11.98,Main,dai,0000,0000,0000,,Can't put it... into words.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.33,0:11:25.48,Flashback,gin,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.98,0:11:26.99,Flashback,taka,0000,0000,0000,,Why what?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.99,0:11:31.05,Flashback,gin,0000,0000,0000,,Takako, you're trying to leave me \Nand her alone together, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.05,0:11:32.64,Flashback,taka,0000,0000,0000,,I sure am!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.64,0:11:35.91,Flashback,taka,0000,0000,0000,,She needs your spirit, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.91,0:11:37.00,Flashback,todo,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.50,0:11:41.26,Flashback,todo,0000,0000,0000,,She's your child!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.51,0:11:43.21,Flashback,shira,0000,0000,0000,,Ow.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.16,0:11:48.27,Flashback,gin,0000,0000,0000,,You can't do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.67,0:11:55.45,Flashback,shira,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.75,0:12:02.00,Main,kana,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.51,0:12:06.72,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.61,0:12:12.16,Main,gin,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to know how you feel... about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.47,0:12:15.75,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want me to tell you that I hate you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.77,0:12:20.34,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,I don't hate you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.32,0:12:26.31,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,When my mother decided to \Njoin the civilian expedition,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.31,0:12:27.85,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,she told me over and over again...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.80,0:12:31.22,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,that an Antarctic expedition \Ncan be dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.14,0:12:35.27,Flashback,shira,0000,0000,0000,,But you're still going, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.92,0:12:38.63,Flashback,taka,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.59,0:12:47.91,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,I was fully aware of the kind \Nof place Antarctica was.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.03,0:12:52.15,Main,gin,0000,0000,0000,,But I was the team captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.15,0:12:53.88,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,Did you make a mistake?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.58,0:12:59.04,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,Was my mother left in Antarctica \Nbecause of poor judgment on your part?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.06,0:13:01.42,Main,gin,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't have any other choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.70,0:13:04.55,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,Then isn't that enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.39,0:13:07.24,Main,gin,0000,0000,0000,,Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.03,0:13:09.43,Main,gin,0000,0000,0000,,Let me just ask one more question.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.51,0:13:12.93,Main,gin,0000,0000,0000,,Is that how you really feel?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.21,0:13:17.06,Main,gin,0000,0000,0000,,You really feel that way?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.77,0:13:20.19,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.65,0:13:24.96,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,This is why I didn't want to talk about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.56,0:13:29.23,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,I have no idea how I feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.60,0:13:32.96,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,All I know... is that, even though \Nmy mom wasn't coming home,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.51,0:13:35.83,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,that day after day, my life \Nwasn't going to change...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.78,0:13:44.58,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,I lived every one of those days \Nwaiting for her to come home,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.58,0:13:46.09,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,but nothing changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.09,0:13:49.27,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,I told myself, day after day after day,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.84,0:13:52.75,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,that it was like I was waiting \Nfor her to come home.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.69,0:13:58.82,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,If I want to change things, \NI just have to go...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.66,0:14:00.91,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,to where my mother is,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.74,0:14:03.73,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,to the place further than the universe.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.91,0:14:10.01,Main,all,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.49,0:14:12.04,Main,man,0000,0000,0000,,All, slow astern.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.27,0:14:13.92,Main,man,0000,0000,0000,,All, slow astern.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.92,0:14:15.04,Main,muka,0000,0000,0000,,It finally happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.04,0:14:16.30,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.30,0:14:18.17,Main,gin,0000,0000,0000,,We hit some fast ice.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.61,0:14:19.50,Main,gin,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to ram through it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.29,0:14:21.50,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,You're right!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.27,0:14:24.63,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to slam down on the ice?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.63,0:14:27.01,Main,kana,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. We'll back up once, and then...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.01,0:14:28.29,Main,man,0000,0000,0000,,All, stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.29,0:14:30.01,Main,man,0000,0000,0000,,All, slow ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.62,0:14:31.72,Main,man,0000,0000,0000,,All, stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.72,0:14:32.99,Main,man,0000,0000,0000,,All, slow ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.99,0:14:34.21,Main,gin,0000,0000,0000,,We'll slam the ice...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.16,0:14:37.60,Main,gin,0000,0000,0000,,with all we've got.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.26,0:14:48.52,Main,gin,0000,0000,0000,,We use the weight of the \Nboat to shatter the ice.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.85,0:14:53.62,Main,kana,0000,0000,0000,,That's why we call it an icebreaker.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.26,0:14:56.59,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,What happens if the ice doesn't break?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.59,0:14:58.33,Main,kana,0000,0000,0000,,We'll do it over and over again.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.33,0:15:00.50,Main,kana,0000,0000,0000,,Again and again until it breaks.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.69,0:15:04.09,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Antarctica is tough, huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.09,0:15:08.50,Main,kana,0000,0000,0000,,It's said that it's especially \Ndifficult to reach land from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.50,0:15:10.09,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,Is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.09,0:15:12.66,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Then why did we specifically come here?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.66,0:15:14.48,Main,kana,0000,0000,0000,,It's the only place we can go.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.34,0:15:19.59,Flashback,kana,0000,0000,0000,,Rules about Antarctic \Nexploration were formalized
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.59,0:15:21.73,Flashback,kana,0000,0000,0000,,after the second World War...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.01,0:15:24.09,Flashback,kana,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, do you know about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.09,0:15:25.29,Flashback,shira,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.59,0:15:30.91,Main,gin,0000,0000,0000,,Japan had lost the war, \Nso many countries were opposed
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.91,0:15:33.21,Main,gin,0000,0000,0000,,to Japan sending expeditions to Antarctica.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.39,0:15:38.15,Main,kana,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, Japan didn't have much \Ninfluence over the discussion.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.15,0:15:42.28,Main,kana,0000,0000,0000,,In the end, we were allotted \NEast Ongul Island,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.28,0:15:44.63,Main,kana,0000,0000,0000,,which was even said to be unreachable.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.63,0:15:46.38,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,You mean, they bullied you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.38,0:15:49.37,Main,kana,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not sure if I'd go that far...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.37,0:15:53.32,Main,kana,0000,0000,0000,,but maybe that is what it amounted to.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.83,0:15:57.48,Main,kana,0000,0000,0000,,An "If you really want to go there, \Ngo ahead and try" kind of thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.27,0:15:59.77,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,That's very annoying.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.77,0:16:02.39,Main,kana,0000,0000,0000,,But that just fired up everyone even more!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.41,0:16:06.43,Flashback,gin,0000,0000,0000,,They raised large amounts of \Nmoney from all over the country,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.78,0:16:10.77,Flashback,gin,0000,0000,0000,,and the shipwrights worked as hard as \Nthey could to design and build a ship...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.37,0:16:12.40,Flashback,shira,0000,0000,0000,,What then?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.00,0:16:15.42,Flashback,gin,0000,0000,0000,,Time and time again,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.74,0:16:18.45,Flashback,gin,0000,0000,0000,,they found themselves on the brink of giving \Nup, but they dug deep and pressed on.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.09,0:16:20.61,Flashback,gin,0000,0000,0000,,Just like breaking through the ice.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.69,0:16:23.83,Main,kana,0000,0000,0000,,Step by step.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.44,0:16:27.13,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,Again and again...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.67,0:16:36.89,Main,muka,0000,0000,0000,,Two-thirds ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.55,0:16:40.39,Main,gin,0000,0000,0000,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.48,0:16:41.39,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.39,0:16:43.64,Main,both,0000,0000,0000,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.19,0:16:52.24,Flashback,taka,0000,0000,0000,,Get 'em!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.77,0:16:59.66,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,We did it...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.06,0:17:04.56,Main,gin,0000,0000,0000,,Not yet. There's a long way \Nto go until we get there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.94,0:17:07.25,Main,gin,0000,0000,0000,,Year after year. Again and again...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.00,0:17:09.25,Flashback,taka,0000,0000,0000,,I'm home!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.72,0:17:21.35,Main,gin,0000,0000,0000,,Again and again.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.67,0:17:25.60,Flashback,gin,0000,0000,0000,,Takako!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.98,0:17:27.10,Flashback,gin,0000,0000,0000,,Takako!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.71,0:17:29.61,Flashback,man,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.61,0:17:31.20,Flashback,gin,0000,0000,0000,,Takako!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.20,0:17:31.61,Flashback,man,0000,0000,0000,,Kobuchizawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.80,0:17:43.13,Flashback_Italics,taka,0000,0000,0000,,It's beautiful...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.25,0:17:46.37,Flashback,gin,0000,0000,0000,,Takako!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.91,0:17:50.33,Flashback_Italics,taka,0000,0000,0000,,It's so...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.69,0:17:52.74,Flashback_Italics,taka,0000,0000,0000,,very beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.27,0:18:05.15,Main,toshi,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.20,0:18:25.36,Main,toshi,0000,0000,0000,,Just for the record, I was \Nreally, really, really serious!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.36,0:18:27.54,Main,toshi,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to do something for her!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.86,0:18:29.06,Main,yumi,0000,0000,0000,,I told you, I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.06,0:18:32.52,Main,toshi,0000,0000,0000,,But she didn't even notice me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.66,0:18:37.63,Main,yumi,0000,0000,0000,,An expedition member can't help \Ntheir captain. They won't let you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.94,0:18:39.89,Main,yumi,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you respect that,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.89,0:18:43.46,Main,yumi,0000,0000,0000,,and find someone more within your reach?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.89,0:18:46.91,Main,toshi,0000,0000,0000,,Yumiko...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.62,0:18:51.15,Main,toshi,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Y-Y-You...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.31,0:18:54.58,Main,yumi,0000,0000,0000,,No! That's not what I meant!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.58,0:18:56.57,Main,yumi,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.49,0:19:24.81,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,How did it all fit in there so neatly before?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.35,0:19:26.31,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,It's a mystery.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.31,0:19:28.14,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,What will you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.11,0:19:30.67,Main,kana,0000,0000,0000,,Have you finished cleaning up?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.67,0:19:32.06,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! All finished!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.06,0:19:34.40,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,How can you be so comfortable with lying?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.66,0:19:36.90,Main,kana,0000,0000,0000,,Would you like to step outside for a minute?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.17,0:19:38.30,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,Can we?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.30,0:19:39.39,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Yuzu! The camera!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.39,0:19:39.90,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.94,0:19:45.91,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Is this it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.25,0:19:51.60,Main,kana,0000,0000,0000,,It's just a brief stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.60,0:19:53.56,Main,kana,0000,0000,0000,,Stay within five meters.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.56,0:19:55.08,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.71,0:20:03.80,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Is this...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.12,0:20:06.56,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,...Antarctica?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.64,0:20:28.72,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.76,0:20:33.02,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Shirase, you go first.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.86,0:20:39.09,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,After you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.59,0:20:50.35,Main,all,0000,0000,0000,,One, two...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.82,0:21:01.08,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,We're here!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.51,0:21:04.02,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,We're here!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.70,0:21:05.78,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,We're here!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.02,0:21:07.03,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,We made it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.03,0:21:09.21,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Goal!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.21,0:21:13.39,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Shirase-chan...
